original_title: The Surfer's Journal Biographies: Terry Fitzgerald and Cheyne Horan
overview: Australian surf icons Terry Fitzgerald and Cheyne Horan -- two of the surf world's most explosive personalities -- erupt on-screen in this action-packed program, the fifth installment of the Surfer's Journal biography series. On-location footage combines with candid on-camera interviews to tell the stories of two athletes who rose to prominence in different decades but approached their sport in the same fearless fashion.
title: The Surfer's Journal Biographies: Terry Fitzgerald and Cheyne Horan
